      <div class="col-sm-12" style="padding: 5%">
        <div class="form-accrediation" style="padding-top: 0rem">
          <form action="thankyou.html">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="row form-group text-center" style="padding-top: 1rem">
                <h4>Career</h4>
                <h2>We are hiring!</h2>
                <p class="content">
                  Academie possess expedite career opportunities for leading
                  industry specialists. We are inviting professionals from all
                  industries and disciplines to join our Faculty Member team.
                  The faculties will handle teaching assignments with
                  professional competence.
                </p>
                <p class="content">
                  So, intellectual mind sets who wish to service the education
                  sector are expected to fill in the below form, submit resumes
                  and get an update on the vacancies.
                </p>
              </div>

              <hr
                class="p-3-rem"
                style="
                  margin-top: 3rem;
                  border-top: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.726);
                "
              />
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-4 text-center">
                  <a
                    class="animation"
                    data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#news3"
                    style="
                      width: 100%;
                      text-transform: uppercase;
                      font-weight: 600;
                      display: inline-block;
                      padding: 8px 40px;
                      border: 2px solid #ffb606;
                      /* outline: 5px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.219); */
                      box-shadow: 0 0 3pt 2pt#ffcd5a;
                      color: #002147;
                      margin-top: 5px;
                      overflow: hidden;
                      position: relative;
                      z-index: 1;
                      margin-bottom: -8px;
                      border-radius: 30px;
                      background-size: 200% 100%;
                      background-position: left bottom;
                      cursor: pointer;
                    "
                  >
                    <div class="meta hover-pointer text-center">
                      Join Faculty Member Team
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div
                class="row text-center content collapse"
                id="news3"
                style="margin-left: 6rem; margin-right: 6rem; margin-top: 3rem"
              >
                <hr
                  class="p-3-rem"
                  style="
                    margin-top: 3rem;
                    border-top: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.726);
                  "
                />
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group text-white">
                  <label for="name" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                  <input
                    required
                    id="name"
                    placeholder="Enter Your Name"
                    type="text"
                    class="form-control form-input-decoration"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                  <label for="phone" class="form-label">Mobile Number</label>
                  <input
                    required
                    id="phone"
                    placeholder="Enter Your Mobile Number"
                    type="text"
                    class="form-control form-input-decoration"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                  <label for="Email" class="form-label">Email ID</label>
                  <input
                    required
                    id="currentProfession"
                    placeholder=" Enter Your Email ID"
                    type="text"
                    class="form-control form-input-decoration"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                  <label for="state" class="form-label"
                    >Select Your Occupation</label
                  >

                  <select
                    required
                    style="margin-bottom: 0px"
                    class=""
                    aria-placeholder="Occupation"
                    id="sel2"
                  >
                    <option value="business" selected>Business</option>
                    <option value="employed">Working</option>
                    <option value="retired">Retired</option>
                    <option value="unEmployed">Non-Working</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                  <label for="state" class="form-label"
                    >Your Highest Qualification</label
                  >

                  <select required class="" id="sel2">
                    <option value="matriculation" selected>
                      Matriculation
                    </option>
                    <option value="intermediate">Intermediate</option>
                    <option value="graduate">Graduate</option>
                    <option value="postGraduate">Post Graduate</option>
                    <option value="doctorate">Doctorate</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-6 form-group">
                  <label for="yOE" class="form-label">Experience In Year</label>
                  <input
                    required
                    id="Email"
                    placeholder="Enter Your Experience in Year"
                    type="number"
                    class="form-control form-input-decoration"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 form-group">
                  <!-- <label for="formFileLg" class="form-label "> Upload Your Resume</label><br> -->
                  <lable class="form-label"> Please Upload letest Resume</lable>
                  <label
                    for="formFileLg"
                    class="form-label"
                    style="
                      width: 100%;
                      border: 0.5px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.287);
                      background-color: white;
                      border-radius: 3px;
                      padding: 10px;
                    "
                  >
                    <div class="row">
                      <div
                        class="col-sm-4 text-left"
                        style="
                          font-size: 20px;
                          color: #39d3ebdf;
                          padding-right: 3vw;
                          padding-left: 3vw;
                        "
                      >
                        <i class="fa fa-upload"> </i>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-sm-4" style="color: #39d3ebdf">
                        Upload Your File
                      </div>
                      <div
                        class="col-sm-4 text-right"
                        style="
                          font-size: 20px;
                          color: #39d3ebdf;
                          padding-right: 3vw;
                          padding-left: 3vw;
                        "
                      >
                        <i class="fa fa-file"></i>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <input
                      required
                      class="form-control inputfile"
                      placeholder="Upload Your Resume"
                      id="formFileLg"
                      type="file"
                    />
                  </label>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="col-sm-12 text-center form-group"
                  style="padding-top: 3rem"
                >
                  <input
                    required
                    class="btn-primary form-control button-shadow"
                    type="submit"
                    value="SUBMIT"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="row" style="margin-left: 6rem; margin-right:6rem;">
